DESCRIPTION:Davis Community Church warmly invites the community to attend one of our Easter Sunday services at 8:30 and 11am on April 5th. The services will be led by Choir\, Organ and Brass Quintet and will feature a Hallelujah! Chorus sing-a-long. There will also be a brunch between services in the Fellowship Hall. All are welcome.
