SUMMARY:Easter Sunday 2026
DESCRIPTION:Join us at First Baptist Church in Davis as we celebrate the hope\, joy\, and new life of the Resurrection on Easter Sunday 2026. Whether you are a long-time member of our community or visiting for the first time\, we invite you to experience a morning of powerful worship\, biblical teaching\, and warm fellowship. \nEaster Morning Schedule\nWe are offering two identical worship services to accommodate our community: \n9:00 AM – Early Worship Service (Worship Center) \n10:00 AM – Community Easter Brunch (Fellowship Hall/Courtyard) \n11:00 AM – Second Worship Service (Worship Center) \nNote: Our Kids Sunday school classes will only be held during the 11:00 AM service. We encourage families attending at 9:00 AM to worship together in the main service. \nhttps://www.fbcdavis.org/event-details/easter-sunday-2
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/easter-sunday-2026/
LOCATION:FBC Davis\, 38141 Russell Blvd\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/P18628652-scaled.jpeg
